{
  "text": "The function T 2.4 (m, \u03b5) may and is assumed to be monotone non-decreasing in m and monotone non-increasing in \u03b5. Another lemma, which will be very useful in this paper is Lemma 2.5 below. Some versions of this lemma appear in various papers applying the regularity lemma (see e.g. the appendix of [CITATION_1] ).",
